Hi Erik,

The error is simple: '\w+' can match 'bar', so there is a collision. The tokens are evaluated by order, so switching the statements changes which one is chosen.
I suggest you use the (%unless ..) modifier:

  field: FIELD;
  value: VALUE;

FIELD: '\w+'
    (%unless
        VALUE: 'bar';
    );

